{"tid":1022582,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"中國作家懸疑教父？ 寫地獄變？ 出日本大文豪芥川龍之介既明言？","createTime":"2019-02-15T06:22:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T10:01:45.000Z","uid":74778,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3324a0047fcbd5769fbb75034333424d44bf4554","tid":1022582,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T06:22:45.000Z","msg":"做乜撚野啊，大陸作家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n芥川龍之介出左個短篇故事<strong>地獄變</strong>，後來出同名合集，收輯左芥川先生幾個短篇故事，如<strong>鼻子</strong>...<br />\n<br />\n我行行下誠品，見到又唔同左封面，諗住係d出版商執過下d字體又出過本新書，...望真d，屌左出聲，...，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國懸疑教父-蔡駿</span></span></strong>？！乜撚野啊？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rx0OZWq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRx0OZWq.png&h=87d76c02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入面又用返芥川龍之介係<strong>地獄變</strong>既名言，<br />\n<em>人生比地獄還像地獄</em>...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A5pW8P6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA5pW8P6.png&h=d1d8646e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以咁嫁咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁狂用人地d名句做封面，入面照寫自己野都得嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ce068b5f747821edec4d863bd904a9baf87789","tid":1022582,"uid":136334,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T06:25:26.000Z","msg":"This is Chi-na"},{"pid":"85169e2e316ce793c05c4b32ae267be7a538297f","tid":1022582,"uid":146340,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T06:26:58.000Z","msg":"講真係可以 你睇完本書如果有抄情節先屌啦"},{"pid":"513db308f3c7bbfb775e69794a092f952ad467f9","tid":1022582,"uid":28451,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T06:49:09.000Z","msg":"內容有冇抄？內容唔同，純粹拎芥川做ref有咩問題？仲要有名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" c